Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.agilent.Agilent33220a, ['VOLT:UNIT?', 'VOLT?',
    'VOLT:UNIT VPP', 'VOLT 2.0', 'VOLT:UNIT DBM', 'VOLT 1.5'], ['VPP',
    '+1.000000E+00']) as fg:
    assert fg.amplitude == (1 * u.V, fg.VoltageMode.peak_to_peak)
    fg.amplitude = 2 * u.V
    fg.amplitude = 1.5 * u.V, fg.VoltageMode.dBm
